OL,6,FA secondary school in Jersey has been
OL,7,Ffound guilty of three discrimination
OL,8,Fclaims against a child with a
OL,9,Fdisability.
OL,11,FIt comes after a case brought by the
OL,12,Fchild's mother against Jersey's
OL,13,FEducation Minister, Deputy Rob Ward.
OL,15,FWhile she represented herself, a top
OL,16,FUK barrister represented the
OL,17,FGovernment.
