OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F381A1767698618
OL,3,CSchool proven to have discriminated
OL,4,Cagainst a child with disabilites
OL,6,FShe adds: "Different things started
OL,7,Fhappening, so they weren't allowed to
OL,8,Fparticipate in the school drama
OL,9,Fproduction, they were discouraged from
OL,10,Fbeing in the canteen, they weren't
OL,11,Freceiving homework at their level,
OL,12,Fthey weren't even being taken to some
OL,13,Fmajor mainstream lessons such as
OL,14,Fscience, PSHE (personal, social,
OL,15,Fhealth and economic lessons).
OL,17,F"They were being taught 1-1 with an
OL,18,Funqualified teaching PA who had just
OL,19,Fjoined the school, and then it
OL,20,Fspiralled from there.
OL,26,@vD@OpmwD@\pn
