OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F381A1767698618
OL,3,CSchool proven to have discriminated
OL,4,Cagainst a child with disabilites
OL,6,F"It had had a huge effect, there had
OL,7,Fbeen tears most days, every morning,
OL,8,Fand my child is acutely aware of when
OL,9,Fthey are being excluded.
OL,11,F"My child sees things happening, they
OL,12,Fmay not be able to articulate, but you
OL,13,Fcould tell that they were so upset."
OL,15,FShe continues: "Funding is a huge
OL,16,Fissue. Each child comes with a pot of
OL,17,Ffunding to cover everything that they
OL,18,Fneed in school. For my child, it is
OL,19,Fjust shy of #30,000 per year, but
OL,20,Fcurrently, there's no audit of how
OL,21,Fthat money is spent by schools.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/13
