OL,3,CSchool proven to have discriminated
OL,4,Cagainst a child with disabilites
OL,6,F"The SEND (special educational needs
OL,7,Fand disabilities) island review said
OL,8,Fthe system was failing, the education
OL,9,Fdepartment didn't implement really any
OL,10,Fof the recommendations from the 2021
OL,11,FNASAN report (National Association for
OL,12,FSpecial Educational Needs), so it's
OL,13,Fnot a surprise my child experienced
OL,14,Fthis, and many other families are
OL,15,Fexperiencing the same thing."
