OL,3,CSchool proven to have discriminated
OL,4,Cagainst a child with disabilites
OL,6,FThe mother explains: "In lessons, they
OL,7,Fweren't able to access the curriculum,
OL,8,Fmy child didn't have the technology to
OL,9,Fsee the teacher's screen, and the
OL,10,Fhandouts weren't enlarged to a font
OL,11,Fthat they could access.
OL,13,F"That came through in negative
OL,14,Fbehaviour in the classroom, which was
OL,15,Fan excuse to swiftly move my child out
OL,16,Fto 1-1 learning.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/13
