PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F381A1767698618
OL,3,CSchool proven to have discriminated
OL,4,Cagainst a child with disabilites
OL,6,F"Simple things could have been done,
OL,7,Ffor example, linking up my child's
OL,8,FiPad or laptop to the teacher's screen
OL,9,Fto allow them to revisit the work,
OL,10,Fenlarge the font and consolidate the
OL,11,Flearning.
OL,13,F"I felt it was used as an excuse to
OL,14,Fremove my child from the classroom
OL,15,Fbecause it was easier.
OL,17,FOn Deputy Ward, the mother states:
OL,18,F"I'm just hoping at the election in
OL,19,FJune, he is not voted back in."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/13
