OL,3,CSchool proven to have discriminated
OL,4,Cagainst a child with disabilites
OL,6,FAll three failures were upheld as
OL,7,Funlawful discrimination.
OL,9,FIn response, a statement approved by
OL,10,FDeputy Ward says: "The Minister
OL,11,Fcommitted to accessible and high-
OL,12,Fquality education for all of Jersey's
OL,13,Fchildren.
OL,15,F"Whilst we do not typically comment on
OL,16,Findividual cases, there are
OL,17,Fopportunities to learn and build from
OL,18,Fevery case.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/13
